Refurbishment project at the Wedge shopping centreThe current retailers, including Woolworths, Seattle Coffee, Clicks, Sorbet, Morningside Dispensary, Wedge Optometrist, Village VetShop, Samsung, Avanti Hair Salon, The Firm and Kong Tai Restaurant, will continue to trade as normal during the construction period. According to the management agent, Mowana Properties, new tenants such as Super Spar with a Tops, Planet Fitness and The Baron Restaurant, will add to the new centre, with its sophisticated design, featuring modern finishes.